{
  "title": "Unfurling Monsoon Jamaican Vegetable Shortening Wrap",
  "description": "Experience the tropical fusion of Jamaican and Indian flavors in this shortening-infused, plant-based wrap featuring a fragrant lotus leaf wrapper.",
