  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion and bell pepper, and stir-fry for 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the carrots and mushrooms, and stir-fry for another 4-5 minutes.",
    "Add the curry powder, brown sugar, and salt, and stir-fry for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in the chopped spinach and cook until wilted.",
    "Meanwhile, warm the lotus leaf wraps by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "Spoon the stir-fry mixture onto the center of each warmed lotus leaf wrap.",
    "Fold the bottom half of the wrap up over the filling, then fold in the sides and roll up the wrap to form a tight cylinder.",
    "Repeat with the remaining wraps and filling.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with chopped cilantro if desired."
  ],
